SPLIT THE DATA TO PREVENT LEAKAGE BEFORE TRANSFORMATION¶

In [556]:
def split_df(df, y_col, random_state, test_size):
    x_cols = [c for c in df.columns if c != y_col]
    # print(f"Y : {y_col}")
    # print(f"X : {', '.join(x_cols)}")

    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df[x_cols], df[[y_col]],
                                                        stratify=df[[y_col]],
                                                        random_state=random_state, test_size=test_size)
    X_train[y_col] = y_train
    X_test[y_col] = y_test
    return X_train.reset_index(drop=True), X_test.reset_index(drop=True)

data['Mental_condition'] = np.where(data.MentalHealth>=5,1,0)
Y_COL = "Mental_condition"
train_df, test_df = split_df(data, Y_COL, 0, 0.2)
